      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "After them the Tekoites repaired — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "The same spoken of before, who, having despatched their first share sooner than their brethren, freely offered to supply the defects of others, who, as it seems, neglected that part of the work which had been committed to them. And this their double diligence is noted, both for the greater shame of their nobles, who would not do any part of it, and for their own honour, who were so far from being corrupted by that bad example, that they were quickened to greater zeal and industry in this pious work.",
        "children": []
