      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "The Tekoites repaired another piece",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". Compare ver. 5. Their \"second piece\" appears to have extended from the \"great tower\" to the wall built by Shallum on the western side of the spur which reached as far as the pool of Siloam (ver. 15). This is here called \"the wall of Ophel.\" Nehemiah 3:27",
